msgid "Plays on every connected speaker at the same time — wired outputs are delayed to stay in step with Bluetooth."
msgstr "Joue sur chaque enceinte connectée en même temps — les sorties filaires sont retardées pour rester en phase avec le Bluetooth."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2975
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2982
msgid "Sync fine-tune"
msgstr "Réglage fin de la synchro"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2992
msgid "If the Bluetooth speaker still trails the wired ones, raise this until they play together."
msgstr "Si l'enceinte Bluetooth reste en retard sur les filaires, augmentez ceci jusqu'à ce qu'elles jouent ensemble."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3004
msgid "Sync delay in milliseconds"
msgstr "Délai de synchronisation en millisecondes"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3026
msgid "Type an exact delay in milliseconds — the slider moves in steps of ten."
msgstr "Saisissez un délai exact en millisecondes — le curseur se déplace par pas de dix."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3030
msgid "ms"
msgstr "ms"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3044
msgid "Calibrate with the microphone"
msgstr "Calibrer avec le microphone"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3049
msgid "Plays a few loud clicks through each speaker and measures with the microphone how far the Bluetooth speaker trails — the delay is set automatically."
msgstr "Joue quelques clics forts sur chaque enceinte et mesure au microphone le retard de l'enceinte Bluetooth — le délai se règle automatiquement."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3069
msgid "Round 1 of 2 — clicks through every speaker…"
msgstr "Série 1 sur 2 — clics dans chaque haut-parleur…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3070
msgid "Round 2 of 2 — quiet, checking the result…"
msgstr "Série 2 sur 2 — silence, vérification du résultat…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3108
msgid "%1 plays in the group"
msgstr "%1 joue dans le groupe"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3121
msgid "Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr "Si cette enceinte joue dans le groupe — décochez pour la laisser de côté sans la déconnecter. Mémorisé pour l'appareil."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3130
msgid "%1 (nothing plugged in)"
msgstr "%1 (rien de branché)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3144
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "Balance de %1"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3153
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr "La part de ce haut-parleur dans le volume — la balance suit chaque mouvement du volume principal et est mémorisée pour l'appareil. Elle n'agit que sur ce que lit ce widget ; le volume par périphérique des réglages audio du système est une couche distincte, jamais touchée — d'où des chiffres différents de ces curseurs."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3170
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3171
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3172
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
msgid "M"
msgstr "M"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3173
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays plain stereo"
msgid "ST"
msgstr "ST"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3178
msgid "Which channels this speaker plays: stereo, left only, right only, or a mono mix of both. Set one speaker to L and another to R for a true stereo pair — remembered for the device."
msgstr "Quels canaux cette enceinte joue : stéréo, gauche seul, droite seule ou un mixage mono des deux. Mettez une enceinte sur L et une autre sur R pour une vraie paire stéréo — mémorisé pour l'appareil."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3208
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3223
msgid "Bluetooth is off or no adapter is available — check System Settings."
msgstr "Le Bluetooth est désactivé ou aucun adaptateur n'est disponible — vérifiez la Configuration du système."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3234
msgid "No paired Bluetooth audio devices — pair the speaker once in System Settings and it appears here."
msgstr "Aucun périphérique audio Bluetooth appairé — appairez l'enceinte une fois dans la Configuration du système et elle apparaîtra ici."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3248
