msgstr "L'enceinte Bluetooth accuse %1 ms de retard — le délai est réglé et mémorisé pour cet appareil."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:538
msgid "Balance levels set earlier were replaced by the measured ones."
msgstr "Les niveaux de balance réglés auparavant ont été remplacés par les niveaux mesurés."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:546
msgid "The microphone clipped on %1 — that balance was left unchanged; lower the speaker's volume and calibrate again."
msgstr "Le microphone a saturé sur %1 — cette balance est restée inchangée ; baissez le volume de l'enceinte et recalibrez."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:547
msgid "Speakers calibrated"
msgstr "Enceintes calibrées"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:567
msgid "Calibration"
msgstr "Calibration"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:568
msgid "The clicks were too quiet for this room — trying once more, louder."
msgstr "Les clics étaient trop faibles pour cette pièce — nouvel essai, plus fort."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:580
