msgstr "Synchronisation vérifiée"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:732
msgid "Every speaker arrives within %1 ms at the microphone — in step to the ear."
msgstr "Chaque enceinte arrive au microphone à %1 ms près — à l'oreille, parfaitement en phase."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:736
msgid "The speakers still arrive %1 ms apart. Calibrate once more, or nudge the delay slider."
msgstr "Les enceintes arrivent encore à %1 ms d'écart. Recalibrez ou ajustez le curseur de délai."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1363
msgid "Two rounds of clicks with a quiet check between them — about two minutes in total. The music stays silent until the check finishes."
msgstr "Deux séries de clics avec une vérification silencieuse entre elles — environ deux minutes au total. La musique reste muette jusqu'à la fin de la vérification."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1365
msgid "Skipped (empty jack): %1."
msgstr "Ignoré (prise vide) : %1."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1366
msgid "Calibration started"
msgstr "Étalonnage démarré"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1423
msgid "All local outputs (On Air)"
msgstr "Toutes les sorties locales (On Air)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:2065
msgid "%1 did not join the sync"
msgstr "%1 n'a pas rejoint la synchronisation"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:2067
msgid "The speaker is connected but could not be pulled into the group — switch the sync off and on to rebuild it."
msgstr "L'enceinte est connectée, mais n'a pas pu être intégrée au groupe — désactivez puis réactivez la synchronisation."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:2068
msgid "The speaker is connected but its audio output never appeared — switch the speaker off and on, then connect it again."
msgstr "L'enceinte est connectée, mais sa sortie audio n'est jamais apparue — éteignez puis rallumez l'enceinte, et reconnectez-la."

#~ msgid "Listening to the clicks…"
#~ msgstr "Écoute des clics…"

#~ msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device."
#~ msgstr "La part de ce haut-parleur dans le volume — la balance suit chaque mouvement du curseur principal et est mémorisée pour l'appareil."

#~ msgid "Volume: "
#~ msgstr "Volume : "
